    The Fib4 numebr sequecne si a sequence similar to the Fibbonacci sequnece that's defined as follosw:
    fib4(0) -> 0
    fib4(1) -> 0
    fib4(2) -> 2
    fib4(3) -> 0
    fib4(n) -> fib4(n-1) + fib4(n-2) + fib4(n-3) + fib4(n-4).
